## Visual Layout Rules

### ✅ DO:
- **Horizontal layout** - stages flow left to right
- **Fixed 600px stage width** - all stages consistent
- **Vertical swimlanes** - stack within each stage
- **Color-code by severity** - visual clarity
- **Separate lanes** for Pains/Needs/Opps
- **Hypothesis AFTER Opportunities** - logical flow
- **Include badges with scores** - quantitative indicators
- **Use hex codes** - no ambiguity for AI

### ❌ DON'T:
- ~~Vertical stage layout~~ (must be horizontal)
- ~~Variable widths~~ (must be 600px)
- ~~Mix elements in one lane~~ (separate Pains/Needs/Opps)
- ~~Generic colors~~ (must use hex codes)
- ~~Assume AI will infer~~ (must be explicit)
- ~~Consolidate sub-stages~~ (must preserve all)

